    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="1、监控与日志管理"><a href="#1、监控与日志管理" class="headerlink" title="1、监控与日志管理"></a>1、监控与日志管理</h3><h4 id="1-1集群状态查看"><a href="#1-1集群状态查看" class="headerlink" title="1.1集群状态查看"></a>1.1集群状态查看</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">kubectl cluster-info           #集群整体状态</span><br><span class="line">kubectl cluster-info dump      #更多集群信息</span><br><span class="line">kubectl describe &lt;资源&gt; &lt;名称&gt;  #查看资源信息</span><br><span class="line">kubectl get pod&lt;Pod名称&gt; --watch #查看资源信息，实时刷新</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">kubectl get cs               #查看master组件状态</span><br><span class="line">kubectl get node             #查看node状态</span><br><span class="line">kubectl cluster-info dump    #集群详细信息</span><br><span class="line">kubectl api-resources        #查看所有资源</span><br><span class="line">kubectl get apiservice       #查看apiserver聚合层注册信息</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="1-2-监控集群资源利用率"><a href="#1-2-监控集群资源利用率" class="headerlink" title="1.2 监控集群资源利用率"></a>1.2 监控集群资源利用率</h4><p><img src="C:\Users\Administrator\Desktop\1.png" alt="1"></p><p><strong>heapster</strong>  </p><p>用于汇总所有node节点资源利用率（已被废弃，现使用metrics-server）</p><p><strong>metrics-server</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Metrics Server是一个集群范围的资源使用情况的数据聚合器。作为一 个应用部署在集群中。Metric server从每个节点上Kubelet API收集指 标，通过Kubernetes聚合器注册在Master APIServer中</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>Metrics Server部署</strong> </p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">wget https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs/metrics-server/releases/download/v0.3.7/components.yaml </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">vi components.yaml </span><br><span class="line">... </span><br><span class="line">    containers: </span><br><span class="line">    - name: metrics-server </span><br><span class="line">      image: lizhenliang/metrics-server:v0.3.7 </span><br><span class="line">      imagePullPolicy: IfNotPresent </span><br><span class="line">      args: </span><br><span class="line">      - --cert-dir=/tmp </span><br><span class="line">      - --secure-port=4443 </span><br><span class="line">      - --kubelet-insecure-tls </span><br><span class="line">      - --kubelet-preferred-address-types=InternalIP </span><br><span class="line">...</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">hpa pod水平扩展</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">vpa pod横向扩展</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">- --kubelet-preferred-address-types=InternalIP 以node ip连接kubelet</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">- --kubelet-insecure-tls  跳过tls检查</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">项目地址：https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs/metrics-server</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>**查看Node资源消耗 **</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">kubectl top node &lt;node name&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>查看Pod资源消耗</strong></p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">kubectl top pod &lt;pod name&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>工作流程</strong></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">kubectl top -&gt; apiserver -&gt; metrics-server pod -&gt; kubelet(cadvisor) -&gt; cgroups</span><br><span class="line">apiserver聚合层：动态注册，安全代理，方便第三方应用接入，统一接入</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">/sys/fs/cgroup/ 资源限制</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="1-3-日志管理"><a href="#1-3-日志管理" class="headerlink" title="1.3 日志管理"></a>1.3 日志管理</h4><p><strong>k8s系统的组件日志</strong></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">journalctl -u kubelet #systemd守护进程管理的组件</span><br><span class="line">kubectl logs kube-proxy-btz4p -n kube-system #Pod部署的组件</span><br><span class="line">/var/log/messages #系统日志</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>标准输出路径</strong></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">docker容器日志</span></span><br><span class="line">/var/log/docker/containers/&lt;container-id&gt;/&lt;container-id&gt;-json.log</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash">查看容器标准输出日志</span></span><br><span class="line">kubectl logs &lt;Pod名称&gt; </span><br><span class="line">kubectl logs -f &lt;Pod名称&gt; </span><br><span class="line">kubectl logs -f &lt;Pod名称&gt; -c &lt;容器名称&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>容器内应用日志路径</strong></p><p><strong>挂载出日志目录到宿主机上</strong></p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">apiVersion:</span> <span class="string">v1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">kind:</span> <span class="string">Pod</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">metadata:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">my-pod</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">spec:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">containers:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">wed</span> </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">image:</span> <span class="string">lizhenliang/nginx-php</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">volumeMounts:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">logs</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">mountPath:</span> <span class="string">/usr/local/nginx/logs</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">volumes:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">logs</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">hostPath:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">path:</span> <span class="string">/tmp/logs</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">type:</span> <span class="string">Directory</span></span><br><span class="line">      </span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#需要在node节点上存在/tmp/log  目录否则报错</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">#将日志文件通过数据卷挂载到宿主机目录，这样一来，就可以在宿 主机上统一查看日志了。</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>不挂载目录</strong></p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">/var/lib/kubelet/pods/&lt;pod-id&gt;/volumes/kubernetes.io~empty-dir/logs/access.log</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">apiVersion:</span> <span class="string">v1</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">kind:</span> <span class="string">Pod</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">metadata:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">my-pod2</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">spec:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">containers:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">wed</span> </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">image:</span> <span class="string">lizhenliang/nginx-php</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">volumeMounts:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">logs</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">mountPath:</span> <span class="string">/usr/local/nginx/logs</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">volumes:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">logs</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">emptyDir:</span> &#123;&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2、k8s应用程序生命周期管理"><a href="#2、k8s应用程序生命周期管理" class="headerlink" title="2、k8s应用程序生命周期管理"></a>2、k8s应用程序生命周期管理</h3><p>制作镜像</p><p>控制器管理pod</p><p>暴露应用</p><p>对外发布应用</p><p>日志/监控</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;h3 id=&quot;1、监控与日志管理&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#1、监控与日志管理&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;1、监控与日志管理&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;1、监控与日志管理&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;h4 id=&quot;1-1集群状态查看&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#1-1集群状态查看&quot; class</summary>
      
    
    
    
    
